Diet and Condition Data

Source: R/data2.R
allfh.Rd

This data was derived from NEFSC bottom trawl data. It contains stomach content information and length-weight information.

allfh

Format

A data frame with 1423676 rows and 90 variables:

character Prey scientific name

gencat

character Prey general category (shortened)

character Prey general category (full)
